UK away scheme applications open
UK away scheme applications open
news
Tue 3 May 2016
Supporters wishing to apply to become a UK Away Scheme member may find the following information useful.
We will now be accepting new applications from supporters for the UK Away Scheme.
Supporters should download the UK Away Scheme formand post it back to the ticket office by 5pm on Friday 13 May.
Please note, we will not be accepting any applications via email.
Applications will be allocated after Friday 13 May to those supporters with the highest number of loyalty points.
Supporters are reminded there are a maximum of 650 places for season ticket holders and 150 places for members.
